column5: Strawberry Island, at the north end of Lake Simcoe, is currently threatened by a possible condominium development. Details, and a petition to stop it, are here: https://www.change.org/p/township-of-ramara-keep-the-rural-zoning-designation-for-strawberry-island-in-lake-simcoe-ontario?tk=c7dMsWE6nHDvecM2b3Nv1gK__1j9lr8jRZspVGnCnT0&utm_source=petition_update&utm_medium=email
I would like to support you, The problem with www.change .org is that I get 6 petitions every day to sign that are part of that org.
Unfortunately change.org is much more of a political organization than it is environmental..........just sayin'
